programme.title: Citra: Aku Yang Kau Tinggalkan Ep18
programme.desc: Ikatan perkahwinan antara Nia dan Zaril Ikhwan bukanlah atas dasar cinta. Nia memerlukan wang untuk membantu keluarganya, Zaril Ikhwan pula memerlukan seseorang untuk menjaga dirinya yang sakit. Dalam tempoh menjaga Zaril Ikhwan, Nia mula jatuh cinta dengan suaminya sendiri. Namun, akibat salah faham, Nia telah disingkirkan sebaik saja Zaril Ikhwan pulih sepenuhnya. Nia meninggalkan Zaril Ikhwan dan lari ke Turin, Itali. Takdir menentukan mereka bertemu semula di Turin, lalu mencetuskan bermacam perasaan antara keduanya. Masihkah ada jodoh antara mereka? Apa yang penting bagi Nia adalah Maximo, kerana Maxi sayangkan dirinya. Namun kehadiran Zaril untuk menghantar dokumen telah menyebabkan sesuatu berlaku antara Nia dan Zaril. Pelakon: Ungku Ismail Aziz, Elizad Sharifuddin, Natasya Mahyan, Adam Shadan, Aedy Ashraf, Husna Mustaffa, Roy Azman, Laila Nasir, Safwan Nazri, dan Syaffiq Sahli.

programme.title: Widuri: Sayangku Cikgu Hania Ep5
programme.desc: Pertama kali bertemu Inspektor Fahri Rakib, hati Hania berdetak kencang. Pelbagai cara dia cuba untuk dapatkan cinta Fahri. Rasa malu dan ego dibuang demi memiliki hati Fahri. Dalam mengelak, Fahri juga jatuh cinta pada guru yang menumpang sewa di kampungnya ini. Beberapa kali pertemuan yang dicipta Hania, akhirnya Fahri juga jatuh cinta pada Hania. Saat kasih bersulam, dugaan datang. Hania merasakan dirinya tidak dipedulikan. Saat hati Hania bersedih dengan sikap Fahri, ada jiwa yang sedang menunggu untuk kembali bermukim di hati. Dalam episod ini Hania telah terjatuh dari pokok mangga di rumah Mak Raha. Mak Raha adalah tukang urut di kampung dan emak pada Inspektor Fahri. Cikgu Hania sebenarnya turut suka pada Inspektor Fahri. Mak Raha suka jika Cikgu Hania menjadi menantunya. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Ali Reza, Dayang Areeda dan Alif Hadi.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep19
programme.desc: Aidid dan Suzan pujuk Haryati balik rumah. Suzan ambil hati Haryati dengan selalu jenguk Haryati dan bawa sambal udang kegemaran Haryati. Haryati lalu minta Ummi Fikrah ajar dia dan Suzan mengaji. Ketika inilah terpecah rahsia, Ummi Fikrah adalah ibu kandung Zafuan. Mulanya Zafuan tak mahu mengaku walaupun dah bertahun dia cari ibunya. Tapi atas pujukan Aidid dan Suzan, dia akhirnya terima Ummi Fikrah. Ummi Fikrah buat keputusan balik kampung lepas tu. Keadaan itu menyedarkan Suzan akan kepentingan Haryati. Lalu Suzan ajak Aidid tinggal dengan Haryati.

programme.title: Another Love Ep25
programme.desc: Leyla dan Kenan mengikuti petunjuk ke kemudahan terbiar di mana eksperimen Projek S-1 dijalankan. Mereka menemui fail mengenai beberapa kanak-kanakkebanyakannya diisytiharkan "kegagalan" dan hilang. Kenan menyedari bahawa beberapa mangsa adalah kawan zaman kanak-kanaknya.

programme.title: Ayahanda Ep4
programme.desc: Haji Abdullah meminta Aziz yang balik ke kampung dermakan penghawa dingin untuk masjid baru. Aziz setuju. Haji kemudian canangkan satu kampung. Ada anak-anak kampung yang menderma macam-macam peralatan lain.

programme.title: K-Love Ep8
programme.desc: Tish mempertimbangkan semua pilihan untuk menjadi seorang ibu manakala Sheila risau dengan keadaan anaknya. Frances bersedia untuk pembentangan besar dan Val cuba mengejar pelabur baharu.

programme.title: Terbaik Dari Jalanan S2 Ep1
programme.desc: Ikuti Suffren dan Banni dalam jelajah mereka menikmati makanan-makanan terbaik dari gerai, warung dan kedai kaki lima. Untuk episod kali ini, mereka akan pergi ke Sate 7 Pagi, Nasi Kukus Nasi Kerabu Cikgu Jani, Putu Bambu Raihana dan Delicious Shawarma.

programme.title: Ayoi
programme.desc: Ayoi merupakan kanak-kanak Orang Asli berusia 12 tahun yang tinggal disebuah perkampungan Orang Asli. Jarak dari rumahnya ke sekolah tidaklah jauh sebuah perkampungan Orang Asli. Jarak dari rumahya ke sekolah tidaklah jauh sekitar beberapa kilometer. Setiap hari, dia akan berulang alikkesekolah.

programme.title: Huru Hara S15 Ep13
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Fikhree Bakar, Bito Beto, Aidlia Hilda dan Kid Khodi..

programme.title: Pesan Pada Hati Ep4
programme.desc: Drama ini mengisahkan percintaan antara Yusuf dan Zulaikha yang berputik sejak zaman remaja hingga dewasa. Yusuf, yang pada mulanya gemar berseronok sewaktu usia muda, berubah menjadi lebih bertanggungjawab apabila menghadapi pelbagai cabaran dalam hidupnya. Hubungan mereka diuji dengan pelbagai konflik dan dugaan yang menguji ketabahan serta keikhlasan cinta mereka.

programme.title: Huru Hara S16 Ep4
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai santai bersama barisan artis & Usahawan wanita iaitu Adan & Harith dari Sterk Production, Khir Rahman, Ash Fasryll & Min Luna.

programme.title: Another Love Ep26
programme.desc: Seorang tokoh bertopeng mengambil alih organisasi selepas kehilangan Turan secara tiba-tiba. Dia memanggil dirinya "Atlas" dan nampaknya mempunyai pengetahuan orang dalam tentang setiap langkah Kenan dan Leyla. Sementara itu, Kenan mula menerima mesej samar: "Kebenaran ada di dalam diri anda."

programme.title: Ayahanda Ep5
programme.desc: Aziz marahkan bapanya kerana sanggup menggadaikan barang kemas pusaka keluarga ibunya demi membeli penghawa dingin untuk masjid baru mereka. Hj Abdullah berbuat demikian bagi menjaga nama baik anaknya Aziz setelah gagal membelinya saperti dijanjikan. Mas berjanji akan membantu suaminya untuk menebus semula barang kemas ibunya. Sakit pelupa Noriah semakin serius sehingga Aziz terpaksa membawa ibunya ke bandar untuk dijaga. Mas membantu Halimah membeli mesin jahit baru bagi mengambil upah menjahit. Rahsia Rohaya yang menyamar sebagai Rohana akhirnya terbongkar, Aziz semakin akrab dengan Rohana. Ahmad pula berkenalan dengan Aisyah yang mengurus pinjaman pertaniannya.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep2
programme.desc: Farah masih terkilan dengan kata-kata Lukman pada malam pertama pernikahan mereka apatah lagi Lukman menyebut nama Myra dalam tidurnya. Farah berasa kurang senang apabila Lukman berpura-pura romantis dengannya di depan famili. Budi terkejut apabila Lukman datang ke pejabat sehari selepas bernikah seakan-akan mahu mengelak daripada Farah. Lukman terkejut setelah menerima surat perletakan jawatan Myra yang ditinggalkan di atas meja. Papa menegur Lukman yang berperangai seperti orang bujang dan balik lewat meskipun sudah berkahwin. Akibat terasa dengan teguran Papa, Lukman bertindak mengajak Farah balik ke rumahnya. Farah cuba menyesuaikan diri dengan keadaan rumah Lukman yang bersepah dan seakan tidak terurus selepas kematian Sarah. Lukman cemburu dan mula syak wasangka apabila melihat Farah bersama Nazim di kafe.

programme.desc: Sejak tinggal sama, Haryati cuba bawa Suzan bercampur dengan kawan-kawannya. Tapi Suzan tak selesa. Dalam keadaan demikian dan hanya beberapa hari sebelum "Kebangkitan" yang misteri berlaku, Eloy dan Alba mendapati diri mereka terlibat dalam pengejaran eksorsisme yang putus asa dan hiruk-pikuk, ketika semakin ramai orang diserang oleh entiti jahat tersebut.

programme.title: Assasin's Target
programme.desc: Seorang wanita pembunuh beracun dalam misi pencarian dan pemusnahan terhadap seorang pemimpin spiritual yang misteri.

programme.title: Viral
programme.desc: Untuk memperingati kemenangannya dalam permainan realiti tambahan, seorang gadis muda bermain permainan VR di bangunan terbiar dan mengambil gambar, hanya untuk menyedari bahawa gadis lain adalah sebahagian daripada gambar itu.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Detektif Khairul Malik menyimpan sebuah rahsia, yang teman wanitanya, Aisya tidak tahu mengenainya. Perkara menjadi rumit dengan penemuan mayat dua puluh tahun, yang menggerakkan rangkaian kejadian yang membawa maut. Kehidupannya berubah secara mendadak apabila dia bertemu Sofia, gadis yang berkebolehan meramal kematian orang. Apabila dia meramal sebuah tragedi dahsyat, Sofia mendapat perhatian polis dan juga seorang keturunan usahawan insurans ulung, Lokman Nazir. Tertarik dengan bakat unik Sofia, Malik meyakinkan dia untuk bekerja bersamanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa, tetapi niat baik mereka menyebabkan tragedi. Sementara itu, penghantaran sebuah pita menyebabkan huru-hara dalam hubungan Malik dan Aisya apabila rahsia gelap Aisya mula terungkai.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep6

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep6
programme.desc: Selepas lebih satu abad, Melati akhirnya bertemu semula dengan anaknya, Ari. Ari mula mengingati masa lalunya dan bagaimana dia mati. Melati mendedahkan kebenaran Sigit dan Kusno. Walaupun Melati berharap peluang kedua akan menjadikan dia lelaki yang lebih baik, Watih masih tidak mempercayai Sigit. Dia memberi amaran kepadanya bahawa jika dia bertindak menentang Melati dan keluarganya, dia mempunyai kuasa untuk merobek jiwanya dari tubuh barunya. Sara, seorang detektif polis dari bandar dan rakan keluarga Fadil bimbang tentang dia selepas radionya senyap dan memutuskan untuk menjelajah ke negara itu untuk memastikan dia baik-baik saja. Dengan semua tanda menunjuk kepada Losmen Melati, Sara menuju ke rumah terkutuk itu. Semasa Watih berlepas dari Losmen Melati, dia diserang oleh Kusno. Dia membunuh Watih, membalas dendam pertamanya.

programme.title: The Red Eagle
programme.desc: Pada tahun 2016, Bangkok adalah ibu kota yang rosak, dipenuhi kekacauan dan penjenayah. Rasuah berleluasa oleh ahli politik telah merosakkan nilai moral ke tahap yang paling rendah, manakala rancangan tergesa-gesa kerajaan untuk membina loji kuasa nuklear menimbulkan ketakutan dalam kalangan penduduk kampung dan aktivis alam sekitar. Di tengah-tengah suasana putus asa ini, seorang wira muncul. Dia memburu ahli politik kotor dan penjenayah keji, menjatuhkan hukuman dengan caranya sendiri apabila undang-undang gagal berfungsi. Tiada siapa yang mengetahui identiti sebenarnya. Setiap kali dia membunuh, dia meninggalkan kad nama yang bertulis: The Red Eagle. Namun, Red Eagle bukan sekadar pemburu dia juga menjadi buruan. Seorang pembunuh upahan bernama Black Devil telah dihantar oleh ketua penjenayah untuk membunuhnya. Ketika masa lalunya kembali menghantui, wira yang terseksa ini berdepan konflik yang akan menentukan bukan sahaja takdir dirinya, tetapi juga masa depan seluruh negaranya.

programme.title: Jiwa Taiko
programme.desc: Kesilapannya mungkin menyebabkan dia dipenjara, tetapi bagi Firman, ia juga menjadi pemangkin permulaan baru dalam hidup. Trisya seorang gadis yang mendambakan untuk dicintai, tetapi apabila bertemu dengannya barulah dia sedar bahawa cinta sejati bukanlah hamparan bunga mawar. Freez adalah seorang lelaki yang riang yang hanya berfikir tentang melepak dengan rakan-rakannya dan menjadi gembira, manakala Lara adalah seorang yang bersemangat bebas yang mahu membuat jalannya di dunia sendiri. Mereka berempat bertemu di Wira Cinta, sebuah kelab yang dimiliki oleh Kak Pora di mana mereka semua belajar seni mempertahankan diri dan juga mengenali diri mereka sendiri, apabila Pinto, abang ipar Firman dari masa lalunya yang kelam muncul di kelab itu dan menuntut bahawa Firman kembali kepada kumpulan itu atau menghadapi akibatnya.

programme.title: Alibi
programme.desc: Di sebuah resort milik Malik, kehidupan bahagia bersama isterinya, Zarina, dan anak mereka, Ayu, berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri selepas Ayu mempertahankan rakannya daripada Johan, hingga membawa kepada pergaduhan sengit. Dalam usaha melindungi Ayu, Zarina secara tidak sengaja membunuh Johan. Malik segera mencipta alibi palsu untuk menyelamatkan keluarganya daripada pihak polis. Situasi bertambah rumit dengan kehadiran Ray, seorang lelaki misteri yang tanpa sengaja membantu menutup jenayah mereka. Namun, Ray akhirnya mendedahkan bahawa dia tahu kebenaran dan menggunakanya untuk memanipulasi keluarga Malik. Ketegangan memuncak hingga pergelutan ganas yang mengorbankan Ray. Inspektor Wani mula menyiasat, mendedahkan betapa rumitnya kes ini, Kisah ini menyentuh tema keputusasaan, moraliti, dan sejauh mana seseorang sanggup bertindak untuk melindungi keluarga mereka di tengah ancaman dan ketakutan.

programme.title: Daddyku Gengster
programme.desc: Ray ialah ketua kumpulan yang mencuri kereta mewah dan terlibat dalam kelab pergaduhan bawah tanah. Dia tidak mempunyai hubungan yang baik dengan keluarganya, tetapi apabila adiknya, Remy, dan isteri Remy meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan tragis, Ray terkejut apabila mengetahui bahawa Remy telah menyatakan hasratnya dalam wasiat dan memilih Ray sebagai penjaga kepada dua anaknya Arisha dan Aidil.

programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Vengeance Of An Assasin
programme.desc: The Assassins' Code Patuhi misi. Jangan alihkan pandangan dari sasaran. Jangan tunjukkan belas kasihan. Natee (Dan Chupong) menjadi pembunuh untuk mencari tahu siapa yang membunuh ibu bapanya. Ketika dia semakin hampir membongkar rangkaian rahsia kuasa dan korupsi, dia dikhianati dalam satu tugas, menjadikannya sasaran dan membahayakan orang yang disayanginya. Kini, dikhianati dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling berbahaya, Natee mengikut kod baru Jadi lebih pantas, lebih kuat, serang lebih ganas, dan bertahan hidup. Filem ini diarahkan oleh Panna Rittikrai, koreografer aksi Ong Bak dan mentor kepada bintang aksi Tony Jaa, yang kembali bekerjasama dengan Dan Chupong dari filem Born to Fight (2004) dalam filem terakhirnya.

Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep5
programme.desc: Melati mendedahkan niat sebenar dia yang ingin mengembalikan anaknya dari kematian. Dengan bantuan seorang Bomoh, Watih, Melati akan membawa pulang anaknya menggunakan darah yang dicuri daripada tetamu mudanya yang telah meninggal dunia sebelum ini. Namun, bukan anaknya sahaja yang ingin dibawa pulang. Melati telah membuat keputusan untuk membawa kembali Sigit - lelaki yang dibesarkannya, seorang lelaki yang mempunyai masa lalu yang kelam dan tragis - Melati percaya bahawa di sebalik kengerian masa lalunya, dia layak mendapat peluang kedua. Makhluk jahat yang pernah terperangkap di ruang bawah tanah didedahkan di Kusno, makhluk jahat dan jahat serta bapa Sigit. Apabila Kusno mula membunuh, dia mula menjadi lebih kuat dan mula menyerupai bentuk manusianya sekali lagi. Kusno mempunyai satu misi untuk memusnahkan Melati. Tetapi Kusno tidak bersendirian. Dengan menggunakan kuasanya yang semakin meningkat, dia memihak kepada bentuk jahat lelaki yang membunuh ibu Melati pada tahun 1900-an - Pemburu.

programme.title: Blood Karma
programme.desc: Dalam perjalanan pulang ke kampung selepas bertahun-tahun belajar di luar negara, seorang ahli farmasi yang bersikap terbuka mula terikat dengan tanggungjawab sebagai anak terhadap keluarganya yang kuat berpegang pada kepercayaan karut, serta satu demi satu kejadian pembunuhan misteri yang berlaku di dalam rumah.

programme.title: Perempuan, Isteri Dan …
programme.desc: Zaleha berkahwin lari ke Thailand bersama seorang lelaki lain menyebabkan bakal suaminya, Amir mula menjejakinya. Tragedi berlaku apabila Amir membunuh suami Zaleha dan menjualnya kepada seorang bapa ayam di Thailand. Diperdaya oleh Amir, mereka berdua akhirnya menikah - namun Zaleha mempunyai rancangan lain iaitu untuk membalas dendam atas apa yang telah dilakukan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Obesiti
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Salleh yang berkahwin dengan Suraya, seorang wanita berbadan besar, selama tiga tahun. Tanpa pengetahuan Suraya, Salleh menjalinkan hubungan sulit dengan seorang gadis cantik bernama Zura. Semasa mereka bercuti di sebuah resort sempena sambutan hari jadi, Suraya mula menyedari perubahan ketara dalam diri suaminya. Dengan bantuan sahabat baiknya, Suraya merancang sesuatu demi memperbaiki hubungan mereka.

programme.title: Fenomena
programme.desc: Isabella yang menghidapi penyakit aneh ketika berusia setahun pulang semula ke Terengganu dengan harapan penyakitnya itu dapat dirawat. Hanya mempunyai masa enam bulan lagi untuk hidup, Isabella tekad untuk pulang mencari penawar. Berpendapat bahawa seorang dukun, Labib sahaja yang mampu mengubatinya - dia tekad ingin pulang mencarinya.

programme.title: Masih Ku Ingat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ashman, seorang pensyarah seni lukis yang menjalin hubungan istimewa dengan pelajarnya, Arkhasya. Meskipun Arkhasya sedar bahawa Ashman sudah berkeluarga dan mempunyai anak, dia tetap meneruskan hubungan itu. Bagi Ashman, Arkhasya bukan sekadar kekasih tetapi dia adalah sumber inspirasinya dalam menghasilkan karya seni. Namun, hubungan itu menimbulkan rasa tidak senang dalam hati Azrina, isteri Ashman, apabila menyedari setiap karya suaminya diilhamkan daripada wanita lain. Tidak tahan lagi dengan sikap Ashman, Azrina akhirnya mengambil keputusan untuk meninggalkannya. Sejak pemergian Azrina, hidup Ashman mula dilanda kekosongan dan pelbagai peristiwa yang menggoncang ketenangan jiwanya.

programme.title: Gila-Gila Remaja
programme.desc: Kisah seorang pelajar nakal Azroy, atau lebih dikenali dengan panggilan Roy telah jatuh cinta pada seorang gadis pelajar baru bernama Suziana . Tetapi, pada masa yang sama Suzi merupakan kenalan rapat Farouk,yang merupakan musuh kepada kumpulan Roy di mana kedua ibu bapa mereka adalah kawan rapat dan turut bercadang untuk mengahwinkan mereka berdua. Namun begitu, Suzi, yang mula berkenalan dengan Roy telah mula jatuh cinta dengannya. Ini telah mengakibatkan kemarahan Farouk bila dia mendapat tahu bahawa Roy dan Suzi sedang berpacaran.

programme.title: Tragedi Oktober
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan Wati dan Syamsul yang telah berkahwin selama enam tahun dan mempunyai seorang anak lelaki bernama Shamin. Kebahagiaan mereka tergugat apabila Syamsul terlibat dalam satu tragedi, menyebabkan Wati menjadi balu. Awie, bekas kekasih Wati, mula mendekati semula selepas bertemu secara tidak sengaja, meskipun dia kini sedang menjalinkan hubungan dengan Farah, anak seorang hartawan. Hubungan mesra yang terjalin kembali antara Wati dan Awie menimbulkan ketegangan dengan Farah, yang cemburu dan menuduh Wati cuba merampas Awie semula. Awie kemudiannya bertunang dengan Farah demi meyakinkan cintanya, namun konflik berlarutan dan berakhir dengan sebuah tragedi yang menyayat hati.

programme.title: Tuan Badol
programme.desc: Seorang yang sangat garang tetapi rupa-rupanya takut dengan isteri, itulah Ibrahim. Seorang Pengurus Besar, dia mempunyai seorang pembantu rumah bernama Nor. Tuan Badol jatuh cinta terhadap Nor apabila melakukan lawatan ke tanah miliknya. Pelbagai cara telah dicubanya untuk memikat Nor, seorang yang hidup serba sederhana di tanah perkampungan setinggan miliknya.

programme.title: Sepasang Kurung Biru
programme.desc: Sarina kembali menjejakkan kaki ke rumah bekas suaminya, Azran, setelah lima tahun mereka berpisah. Azran masih menyimpan rasa kasih dan berharap ada peluang untuk menyulam kembali cinta yang terlerai. Namun, kepulangan Sarina tidak disambut mesra oleh anak mereka, Sue, yang masih menyimpan luka. Bagi Sue, ibunya adalah wanita kejam yang pergi meninggalkan dia dan ayahnya untuk berkahwin dengan lelaki lain.

programme.title: Mat Gelap
programme.desc: Rahim, seorang kartunis merupakan pelukis untuk watak Mat Gelap. Dia juga bekerja sebagai seorang penyiasat persendirian yang sedang menjalankan siasatan terhadap satu kumpulan penjahat terdiri daripada wanita yang bernama 'Mama Bosan'. Selain itu, dia turut menyiasat satu kes kecurangan rumah tangga. Pelbagai perkara terjadi kepadanya ketika sedang menyiasat kes.

programme.title: Terbakar Di Hati
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Badrul, seorang usahawan berjaya yang ingin berkahwin lagi kerana isterinya, Rozi, tidak mampu memberikannya zuriat meskipun mereka telah berkahwin selama sepuluh tahun. Rozi kemudian dihalau keluar apabila tidak bersetuju dengan cadangan suaminya itu. Namun, takdir berubah apabila Rozi disahkan hamil dua bulan, sekali gus menjernihkan kembali hubungan mereka. Kebahagiaan itu bagaimanapun tidak berkekalan setelah anak mereka dilahirkan, bayi tersebut didapati mengalami kecacatan. Badrul yang tidak dapat menerima kenyataan itu mula berasa malu, sehingga sanggup memukul dan melontarkan kata-kata yang mengguris hati isterinya.

programme.title: Perempuan, Isteri Dan …
programme.desc: Zaleha berkahwin lari ke Thailand bersama seorang lelaki lain menyebabkan bakal suaminya, Amir mula menjejakinya. Tragedi berlaku apabila Amir membunuh suami Zaleha dan menjualnya kepada seorang bapa ayam di Thailand. Diperdaya oleh Amir, mereka berdua akhirnya menikah - namun Zaleha mempunyai rancangan lain iaitu untuk membalas dendam atas apa yang telah dilakukan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Obesiti
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Salleh yang berkahwin dengan Suraya, seorang wanita berbadan besar, selama tiga tahun. Tanpa pengetahuan Suraya, Salleh menjalinkan hubungan sulit dengan seorang gadis cantik bernama Zura. Semasa mereka bercuti di sebuah resort sempena sambutan hari jadi, Suraya mula menyedari perubahan ketara dalam diri suaminya. Dengan bantuan sahabat baiknya, Suraya merancang sesuatu demi memperbaiki hubungan mereka.

programme.title: Fenomena
programme.desc: Isabella yang menghidapi penyakit aneh ketika berusia setahun pulang semula ke Terengganu dengan harapan penyakitnya itu dapat dirawat. Hanya mempunyai masa enam bulan lagi untuk hidup, Isabella tekad untuk pulang mencari penawar. Berpendapat bahawa seorang dukun, Labib sahaja yang mampu mengubatinya - dia tekad ingin pulang mencarinya.

programme.title: Masih Ku Ingat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ashman, seorang pensyarah seni lukis yang menjalin hubungan istimewa dengan pelajarnya, Arkhasya. Meskipun Arkhasya sedar bahawa Ashman sudah berkeluarga dan mempunyai anak, dia tetap meneruskan hubungan itu. Bagi Ashman, Arkhasya bukan sekadar kekasih tetapi dia adalah sumber inspirasinya dalam menghasilkan karya seni. Namun, hubungan itu menimbulkan rasa tidak senang dalam hati Azrina, isteri Ashman, apabila menyedari setiap karya suaminya diilhamkan daripada wanita lain. Tidak tahan lagi dengan sikap Ashman, Azrina akhirnya mengambil keputusan untuk meninggalkannya. Sejak pemergian Azrina, hidup Ashman mula dilanda kekosongan dan pelbagai peristiwa yang menggoncang ketenangan jiwanya.

programme.title: Gila-Gila Remaja
programme.desc: Kisah seorang pelajar nakal Azroy, atau lebih dikenali dengan panggilan Roy telah jatuh cinta pada seorang gadis pelajar baru bernama Suziana . Tetapi, pada masa yang sama Suzi merupakan kenalan rapat Farouk,yang merupakan musuh kepada kumpulan Roy di mana kedua ibu bapa mereka adalah kawan rapat dan turut bercadang untuk mengahwinkan mereka berdua. Namun begitu, Suzi, yang mula berkenalan dengan Roy telah mula jatuh cinta dengannya. Ini telah mengakibatkan kemarahan Farouk bila dia mendapat tahu bahawa Roy dan Suzi sedang berpacaran.

programme.title: Sepasang Kurung Biru
programme.desc: Sarina kembali menjejakkan kaki ke rumah bekas suaminya, Azran, setelah lima tahun mereka berpisah. Azran masih menyimpan rasa kasih dan berharap ada peluang untuk menyulam kembali cinta yang terlerai. Namun, kepulangan Sarina tidak disambut mesra oleh anak mereka, Sue, yang masih menyimpan luka. Bagi Sue, ibunya adalah wanita kejam yang pergi meninggalkan dia dan ayahnya untuk berkahwin dengan lelaki lain.

Selain itu, dia turut menyiasat satu kes kecurangan rumah tangga. Pelbagai perkara terjadi kepadanya ketika sedang menyiasat kes.

programme.title: Terbakar Di Hati
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Badrul, seorang usahawan berjaya yang ingin berkahwin lagi kerana isterinya, Rozi, tidak mampu memberikannya zuriat meskipun mereka telah berkahwin selama sepuluh tahun. Rozi kemudian dihalau keluar apabila tidak bersetuju dengan cadangan suaminya itu. Namun, takdir berubah apabila Rozi disahkan hamil dua bulan, sekali gus menjernihkan kembali hubungan mereka. Kebahagiaan mereka tergugat apabila Syamsul terlibat dalam satu tragedi, menyebabkan Wati menjadi balu. Awie, bekas kekasih Wati, mula mendekati semula selepas bertemu secara tidak sengaja, meskipun dia kini sedang menjalinkan hubungan dengan Farah, anak seorang hartawan. programme.title: Istanbul Aku Datang

programme.title: Ruang Temu Ep34

programme.title: Longkai
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang geng 'longkai' (tonto atau penunda kereta). Eddie dan Bada ialah adik-beradik longkai yang terkenal. Semua kenderaan yang ditunda oleh mereka akan dibawa ke bengkel Rimau. Walaupun dia seorang wanita, Rimau berperwatakan sedikit tomboy dan lasak. Rimau telah jatuh cinta dengan Bada, tetapi dia tidak pernah berani untuk meluahkan perasaannya walaupun dia nampak tough.

programme.title: Kasut Ku Kusut
programme.desc: Kasut Ku Kusut mengisahkan seorang pemuda kampung bernama Manap yang berasa kecewa kerana kasut barunya telah hilang. Sementara itu, Markos, ahli kumpulan gangster Father Dragon, ditugaskan untuk membawa Suzi kepada ketua geng. Dalam perjalanan, mereka tersesat di sebuah kampung, dan Suzi berjaya melarikan diri lalu bertemu dengan Manap yang masih mencari kasutnya. Ketika Markos menemui mereka, Manap menyedari bahawa kasut yang dipakai oleh Markos kelihatan sangat mirip dengan kasutnya yang hilang.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit Sawadikap
programme.desc: mengisahkan Adnan (Shaheizy Sam) yang lucu, bersama isteri dan anaknya, memulakan perjalanan ke Thailand bersama sahabat baik mereka, Bobby dan Wawa, di mana pelbagai lagi pengembaraan menanti.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit Generasi GIG
programme.desc: Selepas menyelamatkan Nadia (Afifah Nasir), seorang wanita moden yang telah lama diminatinya, Adnan (Aiman Tino), seorang penghantar makanan, mula jatuh cinta tanpa menyedari bahawa dia mungkin terperangkap dalam rancangan tersembunyi wanita tersebut.

programme.title: Lebuhraya Ke Neraka
programme.desc: Lebuhraya Ke Neraka mengisahkan sekumpulan penunggang motosikal yang kasar berhenti di tepi jalan, dan tidak lama kemudian, kesemua merekakecuali Bobjatuh sakit secara misteri.

programme.title: Love Supermoon
programme.desc: mengisahkan seorang lelaki dan seorang wanita yang menjalani kehidupan masing-masing tetapi sering bertemu di majlis perkahwinan atau parti yang dianjurkan oleh rakan-rakan mereka. Mereka hanya mengenali antara satu sama lain melalui gosip yang didengar, namun berpura-pura tidak mengenali setiap kali bertemu.

programme.desc: Nasib malang menimpa Rio dan Ani setelah kehilangan kedua ibu bapa mereka. Mereka terpaksa tinggal bersama pak cik dan mak cik mereka. Rio dan Ani dipaksa olek pak cik mereka untuk bekerja agar boleh terus tinggal di sana. Malah, mak cik Rio dan Ani juga menggunakan wang pusaka tanpa kebenaran mereka. Mampukah Rio dan Ani bertahan dalam kekejaman keluarga mereka sendiri?

programme.title: Konser Dari Rhoma untuk Irama
programme.desc: Konsert sambutan ulang tahun Rhoma Irama, Raja Dangdut!

programme.title: Cinta Setelah Cinta S2 Ep89
programme.desc: Starla menyangka dia telah menghadapi segalanya, tetapi penipuan Niko jauh lebih mendalam daripada yang disangkanya. Ketika dia terus berusaha mempertahankan perkahwinannya, ancaman baharu muncul. Ayu, yang masih taksub dengan Niko, semakin mengikatnya dalam perangkap dengan menggunakan anak mereka yang belum lahir sebagai umpan. Pada masa yang sama, naluri Starla merasakan ada sesuatu yang tidak kena, dan dia mula diburu oleh bayang-bayang serta rahsia gelap. Dengan keluarganya di ambang bahaya dan emosinya semakin tertekan, adakah Starla mampu melindungi orang-orang tersayang? Atau adakah pengkhianatan Niko akan mendorongnya melangkaui batas yang tidakbolehkembali?

programme.title: Indahnya Kebersamaan Ep8
programme.desc: Indahnya Kebersamaan ialah sebuah program tausiah yang dikendalikan oleh Mellya Baskarani bersama Prof. Dr. K.H. Nasaruddin Umar, M.A. Program ini memberi fokus kepada pelbagai permasalahan yang sering dialami oleh masyarakat, termasuk isu dalam kehidupan berumah tangga.

programme.title: Bidadari Surgamu Ep248
programme.desc: Menceritakan kisah seorang gadis bernama Sakinah yang menjalani kehidupan penuh tekanan akibat fitnah dan dipaksa untuk berkahwin dengan seseorang yang tidak mencintainya. Tidak hanya itu, Sakinah juga dihalang untuk mengetahui siapa ibu kandungnya yang tega membuangnya.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep77
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep1034
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: Dear Mom (M) Ep66
programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: The story is based on a 1993 true event, the "China-Russia Train Robbery" where a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman heads the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: Fight Back to School II
programme.desc: Star Chow (Stephen Chow) is an officer in the Royal Hong Kong Police's elite Special Duties Unit (SDU). During a meeting with his senior officer, Inspector Yip (Deanie Ip), Star jokingly suggests he wish to be reassigned to the traffic unit. Star immediately finds himself demoted to Constable engaging in traffic duty on the streets of Hong Kong. After being made the scapegoat for a failed high school terrorist investigation, Star hastily resigns from the police. He decides to enroll at the high school to launch his own private investigation. But Star realises the investigation won't be easy when he discovers that the bumbling, incompetent CID detective Tat (Ng Man Tat) is also undercover at the high school.

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Young Chan Lok Kwun accidentally stumbles into the Kowloon Walled City while fleeing, subsequently finding purpose amid chaos and gaining wisdom. Bonding with Shin, Twelfth Master and AV, they unite under Tornado's leadership to defend against the villain, Mr Big's assaults, and pledge to protect the safe haven of the Walled City together.

programme.title: WE12
programme.desc: An underground organization, The League of Kaito has been maintaining international order. While 12 elite members possess extraordinary skills and have worked independently for a period of time, they must rekindle their long-lost team spirit to accomplish a mission together to save the world from disaster.

programme.title: Wise Guys Never Die
programme.desc: Nick meets Teddy, a con artiste, when he is sent to prison for embezzlement, and Teddy teaches him all the gambling tricks. After their release, they team up with Teddys lover Lora, to take revenge on Dragon, who framed Teddy for his sentence. Nick though is seduced by Lora and they end up in an affair. Will Nick finally join Teddy in his revenge?

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap

programme.title: Golden Chicken
programme.desc: Ah Kam, a seasoned prostitute, gets locked inside an ATM vestibule with a thief. Both discover they are ill-fated in life and Ah Kam starts telling him her life story as a prostitute, from a teenage hooker to a PR girl in an upscale club in her thirties, as well as being a strip dancer, bar girl and masseuse.

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: The Comeback
programme.desc: Uncle Hua is a retired agent who owns an antique shop on an old street. When the old street is forcibly demolished by the local Green Dragon Gang one day, Uncle Huas hidden identity is accidentally revealed, and he is pursued by a mysterious organization headed by Ah Jie. A fatal duel has just begun!

programme.title: God of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers"; clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: Love and Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: A Legend
programme.desc: Archaeologist Professor Fang uncovers artifacts from a glacier expedition that resembles a jade pendant in his dream. To unveil the truth, Professor Fang leads his team to a journey into the glacier, embarking on a fantastical adventure together.

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kongs toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his familys massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: Empress Wu
programme.desc: Wu Ze Tian is a beautiful and talented concubine of Emperor Tang at age 14. She becomes a nun after he died but has two sons with the new Emperor Tang Gao Zong. The Empress asks Wu to team up with her against Consort Xiao, but is set up and dethroned by Wu, who also kills her two sons. After the Emperors death, Wu becomes the first woman Emperor.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: The Black Tavern
programme.desc: This sword-filled thriller centres on The Black Tavern an inn where the down and dirty meet to plot nefarious doings. A bunch of villains are lured to the inn by a rumour about a valuable treasure being hidden there. After all the backstabbing and killings, they realise that it is a trap created to wipe them out once and for all

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: The Bully
programme.desc: For lovers of the Shaw's sumptuous production and martial arts expertise, this action adventure in the "Jackie Chan style" is a special treat. A persecuted waiter turns to a "drunken master" for help when a restaurant customer turns out to be a kung-fu harbinger of doom!

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: The 36th Chamber of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: The Master
programme.desc: Gao Jian is the disciple of the martial arts master Shi but is constantly being punished by his master for no reason. One day, Gao accidentally saves his masters rival Jin, so Jin teaches him his unique martial arts skill in return. However, Master Shi sees this as Gaos betrayal

programme.title: The Emperor and his Brother
programme.desc: The Emperor Qianlong is not the legitimate successor to the throne at birth, but he only learns the truth when two senior members of a subversive anti-government secret organisation contact him years later. As it happens, the chef of this organisation is Qianlongs younger brother and they must now confront each other in opposing roles

programme.title: The Eight Diagram Pole Fighter
programme.desc: The Yang Generals were ambushed by the enemies and only two of the sons survived. The fifth son of Yangs escapes to Shaolin temple and learns the pole-fighting techniques from the monks, eventually creating his own Eight Diagram Pole Fight and teaming up with the Shaolin monks to avenge his family.

programme.title: Blue Skies
programme.desc: A young singer Hsiao Yun becomes an overnight sensation after standing in for another singer at the eleventh hour. Her success comes at a heavy price however, when her love with a pianist suffers. On top of this, Hsiao Yun must also deal with the unwanted affections from an influential backer of her show.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Boxer Rebellion
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager Cixi believes the Boxers claim that they have developed a kung fu that makes them impervious to weapons, thus declaring war against the alliances of eight foreign nations. The lack of weapons and good leadership in the Ching government allows the Eight Nation Alliances to take down Beijing.

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: Brothers from the Walled City
programme.desc: Two orphaned brothers growing up in Kowloon's Walled City - the place where people are forced to live with indecent businesses of sex, gambling and drugs controlled by triads - take very different life paths. Chin works at a cabaret but keeps away from sins, while Kang is drawn to the sleazy underworld. Are their destinies shaped by the walls?

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Disciples of the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: One of the great Kung-fu film characters is Beggar Su, a legendary Ching Dynasty figure who was also a member of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers. Little-known director Liu Shih-yu uses the best Kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer to tell a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure, as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liangs work, but essentially an image to him as well.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandmas pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chiefs daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: Men From The Gutter
programme.desc: Two very different cops are out to capture a local drug boss. In this sizzling crime thriller, the two cops go about doing their jobs differently - one does everything to the letter of the law and the other just doing whatever it takes to solve crime.

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wens brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wens home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The Generals henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Huns warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

They encounter a dangerous village and Veruca reconnects with her abilities in time to save Klaus, but the two are soon captured by Po and Blade, who are unaware of Verucas rekindled powers.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep9
programme.desc: Slow Boat to England - Po and Blade head to the docks to take Klaus and Veruca to England, and Po tries to have fun with her on their last day together. However, Klaus and Veruca break free and hold Po hostage; Blade shockingly gives up the location of the fire whip to save him.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep49
programme.desc: Small Change - When Puss feels powerless against the threat of the Bloodwolf, the crew asks Callista to help find the mysterious location of the Obelisk of Night

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep50
programme.desc: Little Lamb - When Puss and Dulcinea tracked down the Grotto of Riches, they each have their own plan on how to convince Mary and her flock to help find the Obelisk

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep49
programme.desc: Lucky and the Girl Who Cried Wolf - While Lucky and Spirit continue to explore a life in the circus, best friends Pru and Abigail set out to lasso in their friend back home. With new frontiers, new sights, and new friends the PALs ride free like never-before on wild circus adventures only to realize that there's no place like home.

programme.title: Spirit Riding Free Ep50
programme.desc: Lucky and the Endless Possibilities - While Lucky and Spirit continue to explore a life in the circus, best friends Pru and Abigail set out to lasso in their friend back home. programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep25
programme.desc: Peril Patch / Sibling Quibbling - When a mysterious, dangerous mini-golf course blooms in Troll Village, the Trolls must figure out how to destroy it/Satin's relationship with Chenille is tested when she befriends an extreme sports-loving Troll

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep25
programme.desc: Memory Spark / Wondertusk - Kelps learns about memory spark in an attempt to relive a memory of his grandmother. / Kelp and the underwater gang put on a show to showcase their imaginary sparks. As she practices, however, Scallop becomes convinced her tusk has a real spark!

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep25
programme.desc: The Pawston Chewbilee / Dont Go, Cat. Go! - Based on PD Eastman's classic childrens book, Go, Dog. Go! Follows 6-year-old dog, Tag Barker, on her hilarious adventures in the city of Pawston, a fun-loving community of dogs on the go. Tag is a skilled mechanic and loves anything that goes. With her ingenuity and creativity, Tag can go as far as any plan will take her, always with her best friend, Scooch Pooch, by her side. Scoochs easy-going nature is the perfect counterbalance to Tags high-octane energy. But as much as Tag loves to go, shes often reminded that it's family, friends and neighbors that really fuel a community.

programme.title: Team Zenko Go Ep3
programme.desc: You (Don't) Snooze, You Lose / Save The Squasher - When the crew takes on a mission to help Ian get some rest for a Badminton Tournament, Jax realises that the biggest approach isn't always the best approach. / When Lula loses her comic book, Ari learns that the best heroes rely on teamwork and not gadgets.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep25
programme.desc: Belly Flop - The Riders have to save Elbone when he's swallowed by a giant Sea Gronckle, and Dak's awful cooking might be just the thing to do it.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep25
programme.desc: Coronation of the Iron Goddess - When things don't quite go according to plan, Po and the Kids must rally with other allies to save the Empress and protect China.

programme.title: Abominable and The Invisible City Ep7
programme.desc: Yeti Superstitious - Right before basketball tryouts, Peng learns from NaiNai that it is his big bad year on the zodiac calendar which means bad luck. Peng is skeptical at first, but after seeing the positive effects of adhering to NaiNais superstitions, he dives headfirst into learning all he can to secure his spot on the team. Eventually, he becomes so consumed that he breaks up with Yi and Jin because of their zodiac incompatibility. Cut from tryouts, Peng eventually realizes with the help of his friends that he went overboard and he has more to offer than just basketball.

programme.title: Abominable and The Invisible City Ep8
programme.desc: Toad-al Recall - A wish-granting toad drops into Yi and the crews life just as the dumpling shop is being reviewed by a food magazine writer. Overwhelmed by her efforts to help her mom and NaiNai in the shop, Yi asks the toad to spit up helpful items but Jin and Peng arent so selfless. As a result of granting an abundance of wishes for the whole crew, the toad becomes too weak to continue. Realizing the error of their ways and why the toad appeared in the first place, Yi and Everest use their magic to reverse the toads magic onto himself so he can wish himself home.

programme.title: Dragons: Defenders of Berk Ep3
programme.desc: The Night And the Fury - The kids go on a training mission on Dragon Island, where Hiccup runs into an old enemy Dagur!

programme.title: Dragons: Defenders of Berk Ep4
programme.desc: Tunnel Vision - When the towns well runs dry, Hiccup and Toothless discover a group of baby Whispering Death dragons living in the tunnels underneath, planted there by Alvin.

programme.title: Dragons: Defenders of Berk Ep5
programme.desc: Race to Fireworm Island - Snotlout is concerned when his dragons flame goes out and the kids have to figure out how to reignite it before its too late.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep75
programme.desc: North of the Border - With his identity as a fugitive businessman exposed, Boss Baby has been hiding out in the lawless land of Canada. But hes forced back into action over a new crisis with Baby Love: several criminals have copycatted Bosss fugitive strategy, somehow turning themselves into babies to hide out from the law. While Tina works on exposing these new fake baby criminals to the world, Boss makes a dangerous journey across Canada to sneak back over the U.S. border.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep76
programme.desc: Intensive Purposes - After getting caught at the border, Boss, Tim, JJ, and Pip have to organize an escape from a former novelty restaurant turned interrogation facility using only the four phone calls theyve been given. Meanwhile, Tina has a plan for Dez to infiltrate the criminal baby organization to break them up from the inside, but its complicated when Tinas new assistant Temp Baby Aubrey accidentally takes over Dezs undercover baby criminal role.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep77
programme.desc: The Unshakeable Bear - Boss scours Chicago to find his old co-worker nemesis Board Member Bradley, his key to cutting a deal with the Federal Agents for his freedom. However, he must lose the tail of Canadas most notorious fugitive tracker, a trained bear cub named Henri. Meanwhile, Tina is trapped at home with her paranoid grandma Yaya, forced to prove to her that shes not a criminal baby like the news is causing Yaya to believe.

programme.title: Turbo F.A.S.T. Ep25
programme.desc: Hard Luck Hardcase / Bee Story - Hardcase follows the crew to the desert and goes to extreme lengths attempting to finally get his revenge on Turbo. // White Shadow loses his good-luck charm and spirals into a streak of terrible luck and the crew must help him find it before things get any worse.

programme.title: Dinotrux Ep25
programme.desc: Drillasaurs - Half dinosaur! Half construction truck! Full-on fun! Watch giant Ty Rux, his little buddy Revvit and the crew come face-to-face with evil D-Structs.

programme.title: Where's Wally? Ep25
programme.desc: Norway Out - Odlulu is on the hunt for the Wind Key so she can use it as the world's greatest hair dryer. But the Wind Key is too powerful for Odlulu to handle, so Wally, Wenda and Whitebeard head to Norway to locate the key before Odlulu can find it. Luckily, Whitebeard is a master sailor and can guide the Wanderers through the fjords. Unfortunately, Whitebeard also gets majorly seasick.

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep25
programme.desc: Postman Pat's Pop Star Rescue - Everyone in Greendale is excited because pop superstar, Brad Lee is coming to Pencaster Bay to perform a concert. Unfortunately Brad's luxury private ship has broken down en route so Pat and Jess must head out to sea in the SDS boat and collect him. Meanwhile Julian, Meera, Bill and Sarah are on the train to Pencaster Bay with their mums to watch the concert. The kids enter into a cacophonous sing off' to decide who is the best singer. Pat and Jess collect Brad Lee from his ship only to find that he's afraid of small boats! Pat heads to shore as quickly as possible but unfortunately gets diverted to pick up a poorly puffin from Chris beacon at the lighthouse. Back at the Pencaster Bay the kids competitiveness leads to a dance off against the mums, who do surprisingly well. Pat finally manages to get the poorly puffin ashore to be treated by Amy the vet and Brad Lee goes on to perform a blistering concert by the seaside!

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep25
programme.desc: Clangy Bangy Crocky - Crocky has got his foot stuck in a bucket, which makes lots of noise every time he walks. It's great fun making lots of noise at first, but soon Crocky tires of the bucket stuck on his foot. How can Raa Raa and the other jungle animals help Crocky remove the bucket?

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep25
programme.desc: The Case Of The Rules Of The Game - Pat Pat and the pirates have fallen out over who has won board game and as they've lost the rules they can't agree. They both think they are the winner and refuse to talk to one another. Noddy needs to find the missing rules or they might never be friends again! Noddy launches his investigation and asking the who, what, where, when, why and how questions he follows the clues and eventually finds the rules in Smartysaurus's dinolab. They were blown there by the wind from the Daisy Mill at the farm. Now the pirates and Pat-Pat can agree on who has won the game and are friends again. Good job, Noddy!

programme.title: Fifi and the Flowertots Ep77
programme.desc: Fifi's Busy Day - Fifi has been so busy helping everybody else she hasn't had time to tidy her own garden. Bumble asks the other tots to help him tidy his best friend's garden as a surprise for Fifi

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep26
programme.desc: Clamshell Day - Kelp is excited to celebrate his right of passage, breaking the ice with his horn. But when he struggles to break the ice like other narwhals, he is determined to do it the Kelp way.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep26
programme.desc: Game of Horns - At a big town festival, Magnus challenges Duggard in a competition to be chief of Huttsgalor! Can the Riders help their friend keep his helmet?

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep20
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Bizarre Blitzkrieg of the Bothersome Butt-erflies - As a prank, George and Harold use Melvin's new animal hybrid invention to create a creature that's a cross between a butt and a fly. But some of the monster butt-erflies want to eat everything in sight- including the students hiding out in the school gym!

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep20
programme.desc: The Mad Scientist - The Mad Scientist turns out to be an ally called Akna, who has a history with Blade's brother Alfie. And Blade learns another truth about her brother and his mission. And in the course of a skirmish with Klaus and Veruca, the weapons change hands again.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep20
programme.desc: El Apasionado Negocio de la Niera - Frederic makes a play to take over the town's babysitters by instituting "senior sitting"

programme.title: Abominable and The Invisible City Ep10
programme.desc: Chinese Nian Year Pt. 2 - Yi realizes that Peng and Everest were taken by Nian, the legendary dragon-like creature associated with Chinese New Year and hes also taken their other creature friends! With Burnish and Duchess help, Yi and Jin travel outside of the city to find Nians cave. But a skirmish in the cave drives the conflict with Nian back to the city, wreacking havoc on the festival. The crew and creatures band together to try to stop Nian, but theyre no match. Will Yi be able to create magic and connect with the troubled creature without Everests magic strings on her violin?

programme.title: Dragons: Defenders of Berk Ep10
programme.desc: View To A Skrill (Part 1) - Bucket and Mulch accidentally discover a Skrill, and its up to the gang to save it from the Beserkers.

programme.desc: Chef J's Tale - Chef J tells a tale about unicorns sailing in ships on clouds in search of Unicorn Land.

programme.title: Go Dog Go! Ep40
programme.desc: Dogcathalon - Mayor Sniffington mixed up the dates for the Dogcathalon and it turns out its being held today! Panicked, Tag and Scooch rush off to make sure the three race spots are race ready so they can be approved by the Top Dog. / The Dogcathalon Race has officially started! Tag goes into Crew Chief mode, running around to ensure Team Pawston is ready for each part of the race. But with Sam unable to race, he encourages Tag to take his place and win it all for Pawston.

programme.title: Team Zenko Go Ep17
